Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正大黑繁体\fad(500,500)\fs50\be25\fsp5\bord2\shad2\c&HB6E1F7&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\pos(200,125)}统筹 筱宸葭
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.03,0:00:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,保護我？誰要害我？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.33,0:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，不
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,雅斯敏，快跑！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,雅斯敏，等等！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你的本性讓你
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,保護自己的家人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不受你母親今日所作所為的傷害
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只有你能
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止這一切的發生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,300)\fs5\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(0,100,\fs50)\move(340,182,790,332,28,110)}西蒙娜\N阿尔哈拉兹
