Dialogue: 1,0:42:11.12,0:42:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,導彈準備好沒？
Dialogue: 1,0:42:14.20,0:42:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 1,0:42:15.29,0:42:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我來
